title.narrative: Iraq Demining - Advisory Support and Core Funding for UNMAS (UN Mine Action Service)

description.narrative: The activity will provide technical assistance and core funding to the UN system in Iraq, to strengthen its ability to implement and support explosive threat mitigation activities. Flexible approaches will be employed to enable coordinated explosive hazard management, helping Iraq’s line ministries prepare realistic contingency plans, supporting coordination mechanisms in newly liberated areas, while supporting the voluntary return of internally displaced persons
